  "title": "Interior Designer",
  "description": "<ol>\n  <li>Excellent conceptual, creative design skill and trend setting vision</li>\n  <li>Highly motivated with inspiring leadership qualities and collaborative disposition</li>\n  <li>Participate in high-energy, collaborative team and project environments</li>\n  <li>Strong conceptual design and design development skills</li>\n  <li>Develop and implement overall design concepts and finish palettes through all phase of design</li>\n  <li>Strong verbal and graphic communication skill; effective client relationship skills and talent for working with diverse team of designers</li>\n  <li>Extensive knowledge of all aspects of interior design including workplace design strategy and best practices, space planning,programming, color and material selection, detailing and FF&amp;E packages</li>\n  <li>Produce CAD and Revit drawings</li>\n  <li>Produce presentation drawings</li>\n  <li>Produce schedules and selections/specifications and experience with furniture selection and specification, detailing and construction documentation</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Microsoft office, AutoCAD, Revit, Photoshop and Sketch-Up,</li>\n  <li>Expert sketching and rendering skills is advantage</li>\n</ol>\n<p>NOTE: Years of experience: 1 - 15 years</p>\n<p>Qualification and track record will determine applicable salary range.</p>",
